Keisha L. MAGEE, Applicant-Appellant,
v.
STATE of Iowa, Respondent-Appellee. No. 18-0578 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Keisha Magee appeals the denial of her application for postconviction relief. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
